@bitslicker
I've used zip of two reasons, one is out of habit and the other is compatibility since the software for basically all flashcards can read ZIP but not all do RAR.

@SUparJErk
The releaselist on Pocket Heaven has suffered from a major hickup, which I hope will be resolved soon. I have all roms up until 976 but I won't make a pack until I can verify and fix the names of them all. The point of these packs aren't to release the roms them selves to the world, (That's already done.) but too make a complete and reliable manifest of all roms released to the scene. Think of it as a checked up reference library.
